bill_title: add a segment of highway in Jerauld County to the state trunk highway system.

bill_versions.bill_text: FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to add a segment of highway in Jerauld County to the state trunk highway system. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That § 31-4-209 be amended to read as follows: 31-4-209. The state trunk highway system includes the following in Jerauld and Sanborn counties: From a point in Alpena near the southwest corner of section two, township one hundred eight north, range sixty-three west on U.S. Highway 281 , thence east via Alpena to State Highway 37 south of Huron near the southeast corner of section one, township one hundred eight north, range sixty-two west . 300 copies of this document were printed by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.029 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes.
